ildren%20to%20be%20exposed%20to%20sexuality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajneesh%20cult%2C%20founded%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20attracted%20Western%20followers%20seeking%20spiritual%20enlightenment.%20However%2C%20beneath%20its%20tranquil%20surface%2C%20the%20organisation%20harboured%20a%20dark%20secret%20-%20the%20exploitation%20and%20abuse%20of%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajneesh%2C%20later%20known%20as%20Osho%2C%20was%20a%20philosophy%20lecturer%20before%20founding%20his%20spiritual%20movement%20in%20Pune.%20He%20advocated%20for%20unrestricted%20promiscuity%2C%20including%20partner-swapping%2C%20from%20age%2014.%20Rajneesh's%20unorthodox%20meditation%20techniques%20and%20emphasis%20on%20sexual%20freedom%20earned%20him%20the%20nickname%20%26quot%3BSex%20Guru%26quot%3B%20in%20India.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20he%20was%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BRolls-Royce%20Guru%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20his%20collection%20of%2093%20luxury%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20hundreds%20of%20children%20being%20abused%2C%20little%20has%20been%20documented%20until%20now.%20A%20single%20investigation%20by%20US%20child%20protection%20services%20into%20the%20Oregon%20cult%20was%20conducted%2C%20and%20Netflix's%202018%20documentary%20Wild%20Wild%20Country%20omitted%20the%20children's%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20upcoming%20documentary%20Children%20of%20the%20Cult%20tells%20Prem%20Sargam's%20story%2C%20along%20with%20two%20other%20British%20women%20who%20escaped%20the%20cult.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20the%20world%20to%20know%20what%20happened%20to%20me%20and%20countless%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sargam%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20innocent%20children%2C%20exploited%20and%20abused%20in%20the%20name%20of%20spiritual%20enlightenment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cult's%20attempt%20to%20build%20a%20utopian%20city%20in%20Oregon%20led%20to%20its%20downfall.%20Osho's%20personal%20secretary%2C%20Ma%20Anand%20Sheela%2C%20was%20arrested%20and%20sentenced%20to%2020%20years%