on-6680467%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2223%20terror%20hits%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20so%20far%20this%20year%2C%20down%20from%20222%20in%202014%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727660115000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113797645%2Cimgsize-371789.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F23-terror-hits-in-jk-so-far-this-year-down-from-222-in-2014%2Farticleshow%2F113797640.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22BHARTI%20JAIN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20More%20International%20Games%20In%20Kanpur%20After%20'Washout'%20Row%3F%20Report%20Says...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDespite%20a%20rain-free%20morning%20and%20bright%20sunshine%20later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20day%20three's%20play%20of%20the%20second%20Test%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20was%20called%20off%20without%20a%20ball%20being%20bowled%20at%20the%20Green%20Park%20Stadium.%20The%20unexpected%20cause%3F%20A%20%E2%80%98wet%20outfield'.%20Frustration%20grew%20as%20both%20teams%20remained%20at%20their%20hotel%2C%20while%20match%20officials%20inspected%20the%20field%20three%20times%2C%20all%20without%20covers.%20But%20there%20was%20no%20play%2C%20leading%20to%20two%20days%20now%20lost%20due%20to%20rain.%20Shiv%20Kumar%2C%20the%20pitch%20curator%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Cricket%20Association%20(UPCA)%20maintained%20that%20everything%20was%20under%20control%20in%20Kanpur.%20But%20he%20admitted%20to%20having%20confusion%20regarding%20the%20match%20officials'%20reservations.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20gave%20us%20three%20different%20time%20for%20inspection%20but%20never%20told%20us%20what%20is%20the%20issue.%20Which%20area%20was%20wet%20or%20whatever%20is%20the%20problem.%20I%20told%20them%20that%20you%20can%20start%20the%20match%20but%20if%20you%20have%20any%20concern%20let%20me%20know%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20morning%20and%20lunch%20sessions%20already%20lost%2C%20match%20referee%20Jeff%20Crowe%20conducted%20multiple%20inspections%2C%20but%20the%20soggy%20patches%20on%20the%20field%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20deep%20mid-wicket%20area%20near%20Pavilion%20C%2C%20left%20him%20unsatisfied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20damp%2030-yard%20circle%20also%20continued%20to%20concern%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20push%20of%20the%20pitch%20inspection%20to%202pm.%20Crowe%2C%20alongside%20reserve%20umpire%20Virender%20Sharma%20and%20TV%20umpire%20Rod%20Tucker%2C%20insisted%20on%20further%20delays%2C%20hoping%20for%20sunlight%20to%20dry%20the%20affected%20areas%20before%20allowing%20play%20to%20resume.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20third%20inspection%20which%20was%20scheduled%20at%202pm%2C%20a%20senior%20ground%20official%20told%20IANS%20that%20the%20match%20officials%20wanted%20ground%20to%20dry%20up%20with%20natural%20light%20but%20were%20never%20told%20about%20the%20exact%20area%20of%20wet%20patch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMatch%20officials%20have%20asked%20us%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20natural%20light%20then%20only%20we%20can%20continue%20the%20play.%20The%20pitch%20and%20another%20part%20of%20the%20ground%20are%20perfectly%20good%2C%20there%20are%20certain%20areas%20of%20concern%20but%20we%20can%20start%20the%20play.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20want%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20sunlight%2C%20then%20they%20should%20have%20given%20the%20next%20inspection%20time%20at%201pm%2C%20because%20a%20little%20sunlight%20is%20always%20here%20which%20will%20dry%20the%20concerned%20area%20in%20an%20hour.%20We%20have%20already%20lost%20two%20sessions%2C%20next%20inspection%20at%202pm%20will%20lead%20us%20to%20call%20off%20the%20match%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20ground%20official%20working%20at%20the%20stadium%20told%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpectators%20travelling%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20showed%20their%20frustration%20with%20the%20ground%20facilities%20at%20Green%20Park%2C%20leaving%20them%20disheartened%20and%20wanting%20UPCA%20to%20take%20good%20care%20of%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20stadiums%20in%20the%20country%2C%20which%20has%20been%20hosting%20Test%20cricket%20since%201952.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20deeply%20feeling%20bad%2C%20Green%20Park%20is%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20stadiums%20and%20we%20got%20a%20Test%20match%20after%20three%20years.%20The%20game%20should%20have%20continued%20for%20all%20five%20days%2C%20It's%20the%20UPCA%20and%20the%20match%20organizers%2C%20who%20should%20be%20blamed.%20They%20are%20not%20taking%20proper%20care%20of%20it.%20We%20are%20coming%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20and%20investing%20money%20to%20watch%20the%20match%20but%20of%20what%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20fan%20from%20Fatehpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20fan%20from%20Kanpur%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EYe%20Green%20Park%20ko%20kuch%20ni%20milna%20chahie%2C%20yahan%20sab%20gadbad%20chal%20raha%20hai.%20Mahaul%20aisa%20banate%20hain%20jaise%20kitni%20suvidhaein%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E%20but%20they%20can't%20even%20conduct%20a%20match%20on%20a%20day%20when%20it%20was%20a%20proper%20sunny.%20Green%20Park%20shouldn't%20get%20a%20match%2C%20I%20am%20happy%20to%20travel%20to%20Lucknow%20or%20Varanasi%20but%20not%20Green%20Park.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teams%20had%20played%20only%2035%20overs%20in%20the%20entire%20match%20so%20far%2C%20with%20Bangladesh%20standing%20at%20107%20for%203.%20The%20delay%20has%20sparked%20fresh%20criticism%20of%20the%20stadium's%20drainage%20system%2C%20with%20questions%20raised%20on%20its%20readiness%20to%20host%20international%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20rain%20hampered%20the%20proceedings%20on%20day%20one%2C%20ground%20staff%20worked%20to%20dry%20the%20surface%20by%20using%20sawdust%20and%20covering%20the%20field%2C%20but%20the%20efforts%20were%20futile.%20Even%20with%2075%20groundsmen%20working%20tirelessly%2C%20the%20wet%20patches%20stubbornly%20remained%2C%20disappointing%20the%20thousands%20of%20spectators%20in%20the%20stands%2C%20who%20have%20been%20eager%20to%20witness%20a%20Test%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20such%20issues%20have%20emerged.%20Memories%20of%20the%20recent%20Test%20between%20Afghanistan%20and%20New%20Zealand%20in%20Greater%20Noida%20came%20flooding%20back%E2%80%94when%20poor%20outfield%20conditions%20led%20to%20the%20match%20being%20abandoned%20without%20a%20ball%20being%20bowled%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20venue%20director%2C%20Sanjay%20Kapoor%2C%20assured%20before%20the%20game%20started%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20guarantee%20a%20five-day%20match%20here%20at%20the%20Green%20Park%20Stadium%20and%20we%20have%20ensured%20that%20everything%20is%20in%20place.%20We%20are%20prepared%20for%20rain%20but%20I%20assure%20you%20even%20if%20rain%20comes%20we%20will%20start%20the%20game%20in%20an%20hour%20or%20two.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20sources%20have%20suggested%20to%20IANS%20that%20the%20Green%20Park%20Stadium%20could%20lose%20out%20on%20hosting%20future%20international%20matches%2C%20with%20Lucknow's%20Ekana%20Stadium%E2%80%94a%20state-of-the-art%20facility%20with%20superior%20infrastructure%E2%80%94emerging%20as%20a%20preferred%20alternative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEkana%20Stadium%20has%20already%20hosted%20a%20Test%20match%20between%20Afghanistan%20and%20the%20West%20Indies%2C%20apart%20from%20being%20a%20home%20ground%20of%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20in%20the%20IPL%20and%20hosting%202023%20Men's%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20games.%20It%20is%20all%20set%20to%20host%20the%20upcoming%20Irani%20Cup%20game%20between%20Rest%20of%20India%20and%20Ranji%20Trophy%20champions%20Mumbai%20from%20October%201-5.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727659980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fsesvlg6_sv_625x300_29_September_24.jpg%22%2C%