aven%20again.%20The%20election%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20not%20just%20any%20ordinary%20election%3B%20it%20is%20a%20demonstration%20of%20India's%20democracy%20and%20its%20strength.%20I%20want%20to%20ensure%20that%20not%20a%20single%20person%20is%20left%20who%20doesn't%20vote.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20highlighted%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Development%20Package%20(PMDP)%2C%20launched%20by%20PM%20Modi%20in%202015%20for%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi%20Ji%20had%20announced%20a%20special%20PM%20package%20for%20development%20here%20in%202014-15.%20PM%20Modi%20has%20given%20a%20special%20PM%20package%20for%20J-K%20in%202014-15.%20That%20PM%20package%20has%20now%20increased%20and%20it%20is%20so%20much%20money%2C%20that%20Pakistan%20was%20requesting%20to%20IMF%20for%20a%20fund%20lesser%20than%20this.%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20used%20to%20say%20that%20you%20can%20change%20friends%20but%20not%20neighbours.%20If%20there%20had%20been%20a%20better%20relationship%2C%20we%20would%20have%20given%20more%20money%20to%20Pakistan%20than%20what%20they%20have%20asked%20from%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20Defence%20Minister%20said%20that%20whenever%20the%20agencies%20investigated%20terrorist%20activities%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20Pakistan%20has%20always%20been%20found%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20government%20in%20India%20has%20told%20Pakistan%20to%20close%20terrorist%20camps%20functioning%20on%20its%20land%2C%20but%20Pakistan%20is%20not%20doing%20that.%20Pakistan%20shouldn't%20forget%20that%20this%20is%20a%20new%20India%2C%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20fight%20against%20terrorism%2C%20not%20on%20this%20side%20of%20the%20borders%20but%20if%20needed%20we%20will%20do%20that%20by%20going%20to%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20borders%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajnath%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20emphasised%20that%20Pakistan%20does%20not%20want%20democracy%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20but%20seeing%20your%20(addressing%20locals)%20courage%2C%20I%20believe%20that%20no%20one%20can%20weaken%20democracy%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20to%20those%20sitting%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20border%2C%20planning%20to%20harm%20India%2C%20that%20if%20there's%20any%20terrorist%20attack%20in%20India%2C%20we%20will%20strike%20them%20wherever%20they%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20opposition%2C%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20that%20NC%20(National%20Conference)%20and%20Congress%20say%20that%20if%20they%20come%20to%20power%2C%20they%20will%20restore%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20the%20Central%20Government%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20bring%20it%20back.%20After%20the%20removal%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20people%20enthusiastically%20participated%20in%20the%20elections.%20This%20is%20the%20message%20of%20change%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Today%2C%20the%20national%20flag%20is%20being%20hoisted%20at%20Srinagar's%20Lal%20Chowk.%20Today%2C%20record%20numbers%20of%20tourists%20are%20visiting%20Kashmir.%20Kashmir%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20terrorist%20hotspot%20but%20a%20tourism%20hotspot.%20Here%2C%20two%20political%20families%20only%20focused%20on%20politics.%20They%20ruled%20here%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20the%20youth%20here%20are%20holding%20computers%2C%20not%20stones.%20IIM%2C%20IIT%2C%20and%20National%20Colleges%20will%20be%20established%20here.%20NC-Congress%20and%20PDP%20have%20only%20looted%20here.%20They%20did%20nothing%20for%20the%20people%2C%20only%20secured%20their%20families%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajnath%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20