e%20rural%20countryside%20of%20the%20Netherlands.%3Cp%3ENikky%20de%20Graaf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%2C%20about%2045%20minutes%20away%20from%20my%20hometown%2C%20I%20lived%20in%20an%20old%20apartment%20building%20on%20a%20busy%20street.%20My%20room%20was%20around%20160%20square%20feet%2C%20and%20I%20shared%20the%20kitchen%20and%20bathroom%20with%20other%20people%20on%20the%20same%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rent%20was%20450%20euros%20every%20month%2C%20and%20that%20was%20almost%2010%20years%20ago.%20I'm%20sure%20prices%20have%20gone%20up%20like%20crazy%20since%20then.%20Most%20of%20the%20other%20tenants%20in%20the%20building%20were%20students%20like%20me%2C%20but%20there%20were%20some%20working%20professionals%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2262e9cba0-3ba9-46b5-a647-be6584d3b32a%5C%22%3EI%20only%20lasted%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20before%20I%20moved%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20couldn't%20really%20afford%20my%20rent%2C%20and%20I%20really%20disliked%20the%20stress%20of%20the%20city.%20It%20was%20always%20busy%20and%20full%20of%20people%20and%20sounds%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20couldn't%20relax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20parents%20had%20divorced%20just%20before%20I%20went%20to%20university%2C%20and%20once%20I%20moved%20out%20of%20that%20tiny%20room%2C%20I%20ended%20up%20living%20with%20my%20dad%20for%20a%20few%20years%2C%20about%2020%20minutes%20outside%20Utrecht.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224416%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20a%20cottage%20in%20the%20countryside%20in%20the%20Netherlands.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d91de41d8d2deb96b9138f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222944%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20whole%20cottage%20measures%20about%20355%20square%20feet%20and%20is%20made%20from%20wood.%3Cp%3ENikky%20de%20Graaf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mother%20had%20remarried%2C%20and%20around%20the%20time%20I%20graduated%20in%202020%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20photography%20and%20communications%2C%20she%20and%20my%20stepdad%20were%20looking%20to%20move%20to%20a%20larger%20property%20in%20the%20countryside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20wanted%20enough%20space%20so%20that%20my%20grandmother%20could%20live%20with%20them.%20They%20asked%20my%20brother%20and%20me%20if%20we%20wanted%20to%20move%20in%2C%20too%2C%20and%20we%20both%20accepted%20the%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e2c4593-2835-49c5-93d5-37886bd80913%5C%22%3EBut%20I%20still%20wanted%20to%20retain%20some%20of%20my%20independence%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20brother%20and%20I%20chose%20to%20live%20in%20our%20own%20cottages%20on%20their%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20searched%20for%20a%20cheap%2C%20moveable%20cottage%20online%2C%20and%20found%20one%20for%20sale%20a%20few%20hours%20away%20from%20where%20we%20live.%20I%20paid%201%2C500%20euros%2C%20or%20%241%2C660%2C%20for%20it.%20It%20wasn't%20in%20the%20best%20state%20and%20needed%20a%20lot%20of%20work%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20have%20much%20money%2C%20so%20the%20cheaper%2C%20the%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20another%20%E2%82%AC1%2C250%20to%20get%20it%20moved%20onto%20the%20land%20by%20a%20professional%20company%20that%20moves%20tiny%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20living%20in%20it%20right%20away%2C%20when%20I%20had%20no%20water%20or%20electricity%2C%20with%20just%20a%20mattress%20and%20nothing%20else.%20But%20it%20was%20an%20amazing%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20me%20a%20few%20months%20to%20get%20the%20place%20into%20shape.%20Now%2C%20it%20has%20everything%20I%20need%3A%20a%20toilet%2C%20bathroom%2C%20kitchen%2C%20bedroom%2C%20and%20living%20room.%20The%20whole%20cottage%20measures%20about%20355%20square%20feet%20and%20is%20made%20from%20wood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20help%20from%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emy%20dad%20and%20brother%2C%20I%20built%20a%20deck%20out%20front%20so%20I%20could%20have%20more%20outdoor%20living%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20cottage%20is%20at%20the%20far%20end%20of%20the%20property%2C%20nestled%20under%20tall%20trees%20beside%20a%20pond.%20It%20has%20a%20beautiful%20view%20of%20the%20surrounding%20fields%2C%20and%20I%20really%20love%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20very%20small%20farmers'%20town%20and%20some%20smaller%20cities%20nearby.%20Depending%20on%20the%20traffic%2C%20the%20larger%20cities%20are%20about%2040%20minutes%20to%20an%20hour%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223350cf0e-4cf7-495f-b407-ce5c25de5cfd%5C%22%3EMy%20routine%20varies%20from%20day%20to%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20my%20income%20comes%20from%20doing%20advertising%20photography%20for%20companies%2C%20along%20with%20stock%20photography%20and%20videography.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20started%20my%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20my%20daily%20routine%20has%20been%20a%20bit%20more%20focused%20on%20farm%20work%20since%20I%20film%20those%20projects%20for%20my%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20trying%20to%20grow%20my%20YouTube%20channel.%20Maybe%20one%20day%20it%20will%20be%20big%20enough%20to%20be%20my%20main%20source%20of%20income%2C%20but%20for%20now%2C%20that's%20not%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mornings%20typically%20start%20with%20waking%20up%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20animals.%20We%20have%20chickens%2C%20horses%2C%20pigs%2C%20dogs%2C%20and%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224743%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20horse%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20cottage.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d91de5289b805d1db47c7f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223162%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDe%20Graaf%20says%20she%20tends%20to%20the%20animals%20living%20on%20the%20farm.%3Cp%3ENikky%20de%20Graaf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20take%20on%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eprojects%20to%20help%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emaintain%20the%20property%2C%20such%20as%20gathering%20firewood%20for%20winter%2C%20or%20building%20and%20fixing%20animal%20enclosures.%20I%20love%20working%20with%20my%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20see%20my%20mom%20almost%20every%20day%3B%20sometimes%2C%20I%20just%20walk%20over%20to%20her%20house%20to%20say%20hi.%20I%20also%20spend%20time%20with%20my%20grandmother%3B%20she%20is%20getting%20older%2C%20and%20I'd%20like%20to%20be%20around%20if%20she%20needs%20my%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20enough%20distance%20between%20my%20cottage%20and%20the%20house%20that%20we%20don't%20see%20each%20other%20if%20we%20don't%20want%20to%2C%20but%20of%20course%2C%20it's%20nice%20to%20interact%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221147b9e1-7df7-40e8-a9de-38883c77f2a4%5C%22%3EI%20don't%20feel%20like%20I'm%20missing%20out%20on%20big-city%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20an%20amazing%20relationship%20with%20our%20closest%20neighbors.%20When%20the%20power%20goes%20out%2C%20everybody%20gathers%20around%20to%20see%20if%20anyone%20needs%20help.%20I%20think%20that's%20amazing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20go%20out%20to%20eat%2C%20and%20I%20love%20to%20do%20that%20with%20friends%2C%20we%20just%20have%20to%20travel%20a%20bit%20further.%20And%20maybe%20we%20don't%20have%20as%20many%20options%20as%20you%20might%20find%20in%20the%20city%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20really%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20sitting%20on%20a%20ledge.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d91de5289b805d1db47c7e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDe%20Graaf%20says%20she's%20content%20with%20life%20in%20the%20countryside.%3Cp%3ENikky%20de%20Graaf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20catch%20up%20with%20friends%20from%20university%20around%20two%20to%20three%20times%20a%20year%20when%20I%20go%20to%20Amsterdam%20since%20that's%20where%20they%20live%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20some%20childhood%20friends%20who%20live%20in%20the%20countryside%20near%20me%2C%C2