Ea%202-hour%20train%20ride%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20few%20days%20a%20week%20and%20returns%20every%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%20US%2C%20I%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhelicopter-parent-son-went-college-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelicopter-parenting%3C%2Fa%3E%20my%20kids%2C%20having%20a%20lot%20of%20control%20over%20every%20aspect%20of%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223528f3c2-4f18-498c-b3e8-20b30eab62dc%5C%22%3EI%20was%20beholden%20to%20my%20kids'%20schedule%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20about%20two%20hours%20every%20day%20in%20the%20car%2C%20driving%20my%20kids%20to%20school%20or%20to%20a%20long%20list%20of%20extracurriculars.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20juggling%20many%20balls%20together%2C%20struggling%20to%20match%20our%20schedules%20because%20kids%20relied%20on%20us%20to%20take%20them%20anywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20here%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fberlin-travel-guide-germany-trip%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBerlin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20kids%20are%20expected%20to%20manage%20their%20own%20things%20and%20get%20themselves%20to%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20no%20longer%20at%20the%20whim%20of%20their%20schedules%2C%20largely%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethanks%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaking-public-transportation-solo-backpacking-europe-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBerlin's%20public%20transport%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20we%20don't%20even%20own%20a%20car%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20my%20kids%20want%20to%20do%20an%20extracurricular%20activity%2C%20they%20take%20themselves.%20So%2C%20if%20one%20is%20ambitious%20and%20wants%20to%20choose%20five%2C%20it's%20fine%2C%20because%20it's%20on%20them.%20They%20are%20responsible%20for%20their%20own%20activities%20and%20let%20us%20know%20when%20they%20wi