't%20love%20a%20good%20bargain%3F%20%E2%80%94%20but%20its%20traction%20appears%20to%20have%20picked%20up%20in%20the%20last%20year%20amid%20China's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-weak-domestic-demand-factory-activity-amid-strong-export-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeconomic%20gloom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Alibaba's%201688%20wholesale%20platform%20is%20a%20standout%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20trend%2C%20with%20searches%20for%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Epingti%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20up%20nearly%202%2C000%25%20on-year%20in%20January%2C%20ahead%20of%20Chinese%20New%20Year%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbaijiahao.baidu.com%2Fs%3Fid%3D1790128439390637858%26wfr%3Dspider%26for%3Dpc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocal%20media.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20trend%20for%20%3Cem%3Epingti%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%26quot%3Baffordable%20alternative%2C%26quot%3B%20products%20is%20particularly%20popular%20with%20young%20Chinese%2C%20who%20are%20trading%20tips%20about%20how%20to%20spend%20their%20money%20wisely%20on%20social%20media.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20%3Cem%3Epingti%3C%2Fem%3E%20covers%20a%20range%20of%20products%2C%20including%20dupes%2C%20counterfeits%2C%20and%20products%20that%20come%20from%20the%20same%20factories%20as%20their%20branded%20counterparts%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20the%20price%20is%20more%20affordable%20than%20a%20much%20higher-end%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20most%20obvious%20in%20the%20fashion%20and%20beauty%20sphere%2C%20where%20influencers%20share%20tips%20and%20savings%20from%20dupes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20post%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xiaohongshu.com%2Fexplore%2F66dbb1b2000000002700722e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EXiaohongshu%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20China's%20answer%20to%20Instagram%2C%20a%20content%20creator%20showed%20how%20using%20a%20full%20face%20of%20dupes%20can%20save%20her%20nearly%201%2C000%20Chinese%20yuan%2C%20or%20%24140.%3C%2Fp