he%20Hermes%20Lindy%20bag.%3Cp%3EXiaohongshu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prevailing%20zeitgeist%20in%20China%20is%20about%20%26quot%3Baiming%20to%20live%20well%20while%20spending%20less%2C%26quot%3B%20Lai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-nailing-old-money-stealth-wealth-look-on-budget-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBI%20reported%20in%20August%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20people%20in%20China%20are%20buying%20affordable%20fashion%20items%20on%20online%20retail%20platforms%20to%20achieve%20the%20old-money%20aesthetic%20on%20the%20cheap%20with%20dupes%20%E2%80%94%20which%2C%20unlike%20counterfeits%2C%20are%20cheaper%20alternatives%20to%20the%20real%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20comes%20as%20China%20faces%20a%20prolonged%20economic%20slump%20following%20its%20exit%20from%20pandemic%20lockdowns.%20The%20world's%20second-largest%20economy%20is%20dealing%20with%20an%20epic%20property%20crisis%2C%20deflation%2C%20a%20high%20youth%20unemployment%20rate%2C%20and%20geopolitical%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f4967c17-08d4-4db9-8e2d-73ea97f6c321%5C%22%3EGoing%20straight%20to%20the%20source%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20just%20not%20luxury%20products%20that%20people%20in%20China%20are%20replacing%20with%20more%20rational%20prices.%20People%20are%20seeking%20lower-cost%20alternatives%20for%20everyday%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20particularly%20pronounced%20since%20China%20is%20practically%20the%20original%20equipment%20manufacturer%20of%20the%20world.%20These%20OEM%20factories%20manufacture%20parts%20and%20products%20for%20companies%20that%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20sell%20them%20to%20consumers%20under%20their%20own%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20buy%20from%20the%20manufacturers%20in%20bulk%20for%20their%20value%20and%20pricing%20on%20Alibaba's%201688%20platform%20%E2%80%94%20even%20for%20food%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20search%20for%20%3Cem%3Epingti%3C%2Fem%3E%20snacks%20on%20Xiaohongshu%20turns%20up%20videos%20that%20show%20more%20affordable%20alternatives%20to%20popular%20products%2C%20including%20Lay's%20potato%20chips.%20Some%20videos%20say%20the%20alternative%20substitutes%20are%20from%20the%20OEM%20factories%20of%20the%20branded%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUniversity%20teaching%20assistant%20and%20part-time%20counselor%20Ruth%20Jin%2C%2032%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20recently%20started%20buying%20off-brand%20clothing%20on%20e-commerce%20apps%20Taobao%20and%20Pinduoduo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20no%20longer%20shops%20at%20retail%20outlets%20for%20branded%20dresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNon-branded%20merchants%20usually%20imitate%20the%20branded%20items%2C%20like%20my%20dresses.%20I%20would%20search%20the%20branded%20item%20first%2C%20then%20scan%20online%20to%20look%20to%20see%20if%20there%20are%20cheaper%2C%20non-branded%20ones%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d3542af5-1aac-4434-95e8-f970a270cb5d%5C%22%3ETravel%2C%20education%2C%20and%20healthcare%20dupes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChinese%20consumers%20are%20also%20substituting%20travel%2C%20education%2C%20and%20even%20healthcare%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETravelers%20%26quot%3Bfind%20that%20some%20domestic%20sceneries%20offer%20a%20comparable%20experience%20to%20international%20ones%2C%26quot%3B%20Lai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xiaohongshu.com%2Fexplore%2F66793c98000000001d01b93a%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EXiaohongshu%3C%2Fa%3E%20post%20from%20a%20tour%20company%20lists%20locations%20in%20mainland%20China%20that%20are%20%3Cem%3Epingtis%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20some%20international%20hotspots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20include%20Ili%20city%20in%20Xinjiang%2C%20where%20there%20are%20lavender%20fields%20just%20like%20in%20Provence%2C%20France%2C%20and%20Xishuangbanna%20prefecture%20%E2%80%94%20which%20borders%20Laos%20and%20Myanmar%20%E2%80%94%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20Bangkok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Xishuangbanna%2C%20there's%20architecture%20similar%20to%20that%20in%20Thailand.%20And%20the%20language%20of%20the%20Dai%20ethnic%20group%20living%20in%20the%20prefecture%20sounds%20like%20the%20Thai%20language%20%E2%80%94%20so%20%26quot%3Bit%20feels%20like%20you're%20in%20Thailand%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22523%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Xiaohongshu%20post%20likening%20Xishuangbanna%20in%20China%20to%20Bangkok%20(left.)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e2abf3bf0250c2149293d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22701%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EXishuangbanna%20prefecture%20in%20China%20(right)%20is%20a%20pingti%20alternatie%20to%20Bangkok%20in%20China.%3Cp%3EXiaohongshu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECleo%20Xie%2C%20a%2046-year-old%20senior%20banking%20executive%20in%20Chengdu%2C%20said%20her%20family%20would%20vacation%20in%20Europe%20or%20Asia%20at%20least%20twice%20a%20year%20before%20the%20pandemic.%20But%20since%202020%2C%20they've%20only%20traveled%20within%20China%20on%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20been%20trying%20a%20new%20travel%20style%20that's%20in%20vogue%20among%20younger%20people%3A%20%26quot%3Bcitywalk.%26quot%3B%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20visit%20a%20Chinese%20city%20and%20spend%20a%20day%20strolling%20its%20streets%20and%20soaking%20in%20its%20atmosphere%2C%20instead%20of%20taking%20a%20full-blown%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20has%20taken%20off%20on%20Xiaohongshu%2C%20with%20over%201.7%20billion%20views%20for%20%23Citywalk%2C%20where%20young%20spenders%20share%20their%20favorite%20local%20snack%20shops%20or%20recommend%20walking%20routes%20for%20their%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20enjoy%20walking%20around%20and%20seeing%20the%20life%20of%20local%20people%2C%20tasting%20local%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20Xie%20told%20BI%2C%20saying%20she%20prefers%20to%20take%20the%20high-speed%20rail%20instead%20of%20flying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20control%20measures%20during%20the%20pandemic%20changed%20everyone's%20travel%20habits%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BNow%20many%20people%20think%20domestic%20vacations%20are%20convenient%20and%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20plan%20to%20do%20so%20much.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20education%2C%20young%20people%20are%20exploring%20options%20at%20universities%20that%20target%20senior%20students%20and%20attending%20personal-interest%20classes%20at%20public%20libraries%2C%20where%20they're%20cheaper%20than%20at%20commercial%20outlets%2C%20said%20Lai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20people%20are%20turning%20to%20telemedicine%20and%20online%20pharmacies%20for%20non-critical%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2293a08222-425a-4a96-9ed7-4b9f7d21d6b6%5C%22%3EChina's%20economy%20is%20in%20a%20deflationary%20mode%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wave%20to%20downgrade%20spending%20comes%20as%20China%20is%20still%20struggling%20to%20turn%20its%20economy%20around%20following%20the%20pandemic.%20Beijing%20is%20now%20trying%20to%20turn%20the%20economy%20around%20with%20a%20concerted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-aggressive-monetary-stimulus-interest-rate-rrr-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estimulus%20blitz%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fchina-stock-market-rally-economy-stimulus-liqudity-overwhelm-system-2024-9%3F_gl%3D1*1s0z3fm*_ga*NzU5NzExNzA1LjE3MDU1ODE2NjI.*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTcyNzQyNDQ2Ni42NTYuMS4xNzI3NDI3NjQ4LjYwLjAuMA..%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboosted%20market%20sentiment%20tremendously.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfficial%20data%20released%20in%20September%20showed%20China's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stats.gov.cn%2Fsj%2Fzxfb%2F202409%2Ft20240909_1956311.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EConsumer%20Price%20Index%3C%2Fa%3E%20rising%20less%20than