nprofit%20keeping%20the%20proceeds.%20%26quot%3BAssets%20previously%20donated%20to%20the%20public%20benefit%20cannot%20be%20repurposed%20to%20private%20benefit%20without%20compensating%20the%20public%20for%20the%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20Alexander%20Reid%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20BakerHostetler%2C%20told%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22774ad3d8-2602-446e-8267-780a70a7b3a5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEquity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20OpenAI's%20investors%20are%20set%20to%20receive%20a%20cut%20of%20its%20future%20profits%2C%20but%20it%20will%20need%20to%20translate%20those%20stakes%20into%20equity%20in%20the%20new%20company.%20Microsoft's%20more%20than%20%2413%20billion%20investment%20in%20OpenAI%20means%20it%20would%20have%20a%20sizable%20amount%20of%20equity%20in%20the%20new%20structure%2C%20which%20might%20warrant%20antitrust%20regulation%2C%20the%20Journal%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c9bd9ba-9e1c-4e2f-b039-72ad3a832c26%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAltman's%20equity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20structure%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopen-ai-sam-altman-equity-stake-valuation-private-nonprofit-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAltman%20is%20set%20to%20get%20equity%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20company.%20Reports%20have%20suggested%20that%20discussions%20have%20been%20underway%20at%20OpenAI%20to%20give%20Altman%20a%207%25%20equity%20stake%2C%20valued%20at%20some%20%24150%20billion.%20Altman%20dismissed%20those%20reports%20as%20%26quot%3Bludicrous%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D07cd1f95bdf78d33dbcb342fc07bca0c4b4adffd58796f04cbf76a4e58006e44%26postID%3D66f9c4b2e5b54083003b27bd%26postSlug%3Dwhat-openai-needs-to-do-to-become-for-profit-altman-2024-9%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.theinformation.com%252Fbriefings%252Fopenai-ceo-altman-says-investors-are-pushing-to-give-him-equity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%