nitiative-petition-17-which-would-raise-corporate-taxes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWillamette%20Week%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%20that%20the%20ballot%20measure%20%26quot%3Bmay%20look%20good%20on%20paper%2C%20but%20its%20flawed%20approach%20would%20punch%20a%20huge%20hole%20in%20the%20state%20budget%20and%20put%20essential%20services%20for%20low-wage%20and%20working%20families%20at%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20united%20front%20of%20state%20Democratic%20legislators%20%E2%80%94%20who%20are%20more%20likely%20than%20their%20conservative%20counterparts%20to%20support%20the%20kinds%20of%20basic%20income%20programs%20that%20have%20gained%20popularity%20nationwide%20%E2%80%94%20is%20also%20fighting%20the%20ballot%20measure.%20They%20fear%20it%20could%20hamper%20job%20growth%20and%20%26quot%3Bcause%20cuts%20to%20critical%20services%20like%20road%20maintenance%2C%20fire%20fighting%2C%20and%20addiction%20recovery%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20state's%20Senate%20Democratic%20Leadership%20Fund%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state's%20Republican%20Party%20called%20the%20measure%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%2C%20misguided%2C%20and%20harmful%20to%20Oregonians%20and%20to%20Oregon%20small%20businesses%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20press%20release%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Measure%20118%20passes%2C%20the%20%241600%20'rebate'%20each%20taxpayer%20would%20receive%20would%20be%20dwarfed%20by%20the%20necessity%20of%20paying%20even%20higher%20prices%20for%20groceries%2C%20medicine%2C%20utilities%2C%20gasoline%2C%20clothing%20and%20just%20about%20everything%20else%20Oregonians%20struggle%20to%20afford%20already%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20said.%20It%20added%20that%20the%20rebate%20could%20drive%20businesses%20out%20of%20Oregon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Oregon%20Legislative%20Revenue%20Office%2C%20a%20nonpartisan%20entity%2C%20released%20a%20report%20this%20month%20that%20found%20low-income%20rebate%20recipients%20could%20be%20disqualified%20from%20receiving%20aid%20from%20federal%20programs%20like%20Temporary%20Assistance%20for%20Needy%20Families%20and%20Medicaid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20were%20no%20changes%20and%20Measure%20118%20becomes%20law%2C%20that%20just%20creates%20a%20%241.3%20billion%20hole%20in%20the%20general%20fund%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Allanach%2C%20the%20state's%20Legislative%20Revenue%20Officer%2C%20told%20The%20Oregonian.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Legislature%20could%20change%20it%2C%20but%20that%20has%20its%20own%20issues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20months%20of%20opposition%20from%20politicians%20and%20business%20leaders%2C%20Antonio%20Gisbert%2C%20the%20petitioner%20behind%20the%20ballot%20measure%2C%20has%20maintained%20that%20the%20rebate%20would%20be%20net%20neutral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20short%2C%20General%20Fund%20dollars%20do%20not%20fund%20the%20rebate%2C%20all%20implementation%20and%20related%20costs%20are%20paid%20for%20by%20the%20new%20revenue.%20The%20reduction%20in%20poverty%20decreases%20demand%20on%20services%20and%20the%20increased%20economic%20stimulus%20will%20boost%20the%20state's%20economy%20and%20lead%20to%20increased%20tax%20receipts%20and%20the%20General%20Fund%20resources%2C%26quot%3B%20Gisbert%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20email%20in%20August.%20He%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20additional%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286ac4ac1-895a-4841-80a4-946e5a5d76ed%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20fight%20over%20UBI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-ubi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUniversal%20basic%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%20programs%20offer%20recurring%2C%20unconditional%20payments%20to%20people%20regardless%20of%20their%20economic%20status.%20Measure%20118%20would%20make%20Oregon%20the%20second%20state%20in%20the%20United%20States%20to%20have%20some%20form%20of%20a%20statewide%20universal%20basic%20income%2C%20joining%20Alaska.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-sovereign-wealth-fund-alaska-universal-basic-income-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlaska%20Permanent%20Fund%3C%2Fa%3E%20distributes%20annual%20funds%20to%20all%20Alaskans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProponents%20of%20these%20programs%20say%20they%20can%20help%20poor%20residents%20pay%20for%20basic%20needs%20and%20stimulate%20the%20economy%2C%20while%20their%20opponents%20%E2%80%94%20most%20commonly%20conservative%20lawmakers%20%E2%80%94%20argue%20that%20they%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiowa-republicans-block-guaranteed-basic-income-socialism-steroids-ubi-poverty-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecloser%20to%20%26quot%3Bsocialism%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20offer%20payments%20with%20no%20merit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20previous%20comments%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Gisbert%20said%20he%20remains%20optimistic%20voters%20will%20support%20the%20measure%20in%20the%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20kind%20of%20does%20seem%20a%20little%20bit%20like%20some%20of%20these%20elected%20%5Bofficials%5D%20are%20more%20beholden%20to%20corporations%20and%20corporate%20interests%20than%20they%20are%20to%20the%20interests%20of%20everyday%20Oregonians%2C%26quot%3B%20Gisbert%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20super%20committed%20in%20instituting%20some%20degree%20of%20corporate%20tax%20justice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGov.%20Tina%20Kotek%20did%20not%20immediately%20return%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foregon-opposition-measure-118-basic-income-corporate-tax-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727648613000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f70446f9f6733e4be07722%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus