20Abundance%20Institute%2C%20a%20tech%20nonprofit%2C%20and%20a%20former%20acting%20chief%20technologist%20at%20the%20FTC%2C%20told%20Bloomberg%20that%20the%20action%20against%20Rytr%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20aggressive%26quot%3B%20use%20of%20authority%20for%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20worries%20me%20about%20the%20effect%20it%20would%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Chilson%20told%20the%20outlet.%20%26quot%3BThe%20legal%20uncertainty%20of%2C%20'If%20someone%20does%20something%20bad%20with%20my%20product%2C%20is%20the%20FTC%20going%20to%20sue%20me%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommission%20members%20voted%203%20to%202%20on%20party%20lines%20to%20approve%20the%20action%20against%20the%20companies%2C%20with%20two%20Republican%20commissioners%20dissenting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20dissent%2C%20Republican%20commissioner%20Melissa%20Holyoak%20wrote%20that%20misguided%20enforcement%20can%20stifle%20innovation%20and%20competition%20in%20all%20industries%2C%20%26quot%3Bespecially%20evolving%20ones%20like%20artificial%20intelligence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeceptive-ai-products-fake-online-reviews-crackdown-stifle-innovation-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727644331000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f9b5847518aa57bc9f0f83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeceptive-ai-products-fake-online-reviews-crackdown-stifle-innovation-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Online%20companies%20are%20selling%20some%20questionable%20AI%20products%20online%2C%20like%20tools%20that%20mass%20produce%20fake%20reviews.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kniemeyer%40insider.com%20(Kenneth%20Niemeyer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeceptive-ai-products-fake-online-reviews-crackdown-stifle-innovation-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpU