%2Fus-renewable-energy-transition-solar-electric-vehicles-hit-records-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenergy%20transition%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20broad%20shift%20from%20fossil-based%20energy%20production%20systems%20to%20renewable%20resources%20like%20wind%20and%20solar%20power%20%E2%80%94%20hit%20%241.8%20billion%20in%202023%2C%20with%20countries%20like%20China%20and%20the%20United%20States%20leading%20the%20charge%2C%20according%20to%20BloombergNEF%2C%20an%20energy%20research%20company.%20The%20International%20Energy%20Agency%20says%20total%20investment%20in%20clean%20energy%20could%20reach%20%242%20trillion%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20shift%20to%20a%20cleaner%2C%20lower-carbon%20world%20doesn't%20depend%20solely%20on%20the%20work%20of%20government%20officials%2C%20legislators%2C%20or%20even%20major%20businesses.%20It%20also%20hinges%20on%20players%20working%20behind%20the%20scenes%20to%20secure%20the%20prices%20of%20key%20commodities%20like%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%2C%20essential%20for%20electricity%20generation%20and%20heating%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffund-carbon-removal-corporates-avoid-bad-credits-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarbon%20offsets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20help%20companies%20counteract%20the%20impact%20of%20their%20carbon%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20Singapore-based%20commodities%20exchange%20called%20Abaxx%2C%20which%20launched%20in%20June%2C%20is%20working%20to%20do%20that%20by%20providing%20companies%2C%20governments%2C%20and%20project%20developers%20with%20a%20transparent%20marketplace%20for%20their%20trades.%20Commodities%20markets%20help%20stabilize%20prices%20by%20helping%20suppliers%20and%20consumers%20figure%20out%20fair%20prices%2C%20hedge%20against%20volatile%20price%20changes%2C%20and%20execute%20efficient%20and%20transparent%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExchanges%20like%20Abaxx%20play%20a%20role%20in%20this%20because%20they%20help%20lock%20in%20prices%20and%20mitigate%20drastic%20fluctuations%20in%20the%20future.%20Abaxx%20deals%20in%20futures%20contracts%2C%20legally%20binding%20agreements%20to%20buy%20or%20sell%20commodities%20at%20a%20specified%20future%20date.%20Three%20regionally%20deliverable%20liquified%20natural%20gas%20contracts%20and%20two%20carbon%20offset%20contracts%20are%20already%20trading%20on%20the%20exchange.%20It's%20working%20on%20launching%20futures%20contracts%20for%20gold%20and%20battery%20metals%2C%20like%20lithium%2C%20a%20component%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-cheaper-electric-vehicle-battery-technology-lithium-shift-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebatteries%20that%20power%20EVs%20like%20Tesla%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJosh%20Crumb%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20founder%20of%20Abaxx%2C%20says%20unclear%20pricing%20can%20lead%20to%20higher%20and%20more%20volatile%20prices%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20consumers%20while%20also%20forcing%20commodity%20producers%20to%20navigate%20turbulent%20investment%20cycles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20look%20at%20the%20battery%20supply%20chain%2C%20nickel%20sulfate%2C%20lithium%2C%20cobalt%2C%20these%20things%20have%20gone%20through%20huge%20swings%20of%20boom%20and%20bust%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Crumb%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20main%20reason%20why%20is%20we%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20market%20transparency%20so%20that%20people%20can%20forward%20plan%2C%20price%2C%20hedge%2C%20all%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrumb%20first%20realized%20that%20the%20commodity%20industry%20needed%20more%20innovation%20when%20he%20was%20working%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frip-goldman-sachs-wall-street-investment-bank-dead-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrategist%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20years%20following%20the%202008%20financial%20crisis.%20That%20coincided%20with%20the%20end%20of%20the%20commodities%20boom%20of%20the%202000s%2C%20during%20which%20the%20prices%20of%20many%20commodities%2C%20from%20food%20to%20oil%20to%20chemicals%2C%20had%20drastically%20surged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20with%20trading%20in%20full%20swing%2C%20Crumb%20hopes%20Abaxx%20will%20play%20a%20role%20in%20stabilizing%20what%20he%20sees%20as%20the%20next%20commodity%20investment%20cycle%20%E2%80%94%20marked%20not%20just%20by%20a%20need%20for%20new%20commodities%20to%20facilitate%20the%20energy%20transition%20but%20also%20a%20surge%20in%20electrification.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20speak%20of%20the%20energy%20transition%20to%20a%20lower%20carbon%20economy%2C%20they%20are%20usually%20speaking%20of%20replacing%20internal%20combustion%20engines%20with%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20with%20electricity%20supplied%20by%20low%20carbon%20renewables%2C%20hydro%2C%20and%20nuclear%20power.%20This%20will%20lead%20to%20a%20dramatic%20increase%20in%20electricity%20consumption%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20representative%20for%20Crumb%20wrote%20to%20Business%20Insider%20by%20email.%20Between%202022%20and%202050%2C%20global%20electricity%20generation%20is%20expected%20to%20surge%20at%20a%20faster%20rate%20than%20it%20did%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20from%20the%20International%20Energy%20Agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20though%2C%20exchanges%20like%20Abaxx%20could%20play%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20geopolitics%2C%20Crumb%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20want%20more%20transparency%3B%20you%20want%20more%20markets%20because%20we%20think%20that%20leads%20to%20more%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20think%20trade%20and%20networks%20keeps%20the%20world%20at%20peace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fabaxx-commodities-exchange-energy-transition-goldman-sachs-alum-2024-9%5C%22%