sis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20requirements%20have%20also%20been%20incorporated%20in%20the%20naval%20deal%20which%20will%20include%20around%2040%20drop%20tanks%20and%20a%20small%20number%20of%20work%20stations%20for%20the%20planes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20side%20is%20also%20going%20to%20get%20more%20number%20of%20long-range%20air-to-air%20Meteor%20missiles%20and%20with%20the%20anti-ship%20weaponry%20in%20this%20project%20planned%20to%20be%20concluded%20before%20the%20end%20of%20this%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727631180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fptaol9r8_rafale-pic_625x300_21_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffrance-submits-final-price-offer-to-india-for-26-rafale-marine-jet-deal-6677687%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22France%20has%20submitted%20the%20final%20price%20offer%20to%20India%20for%20the%2026%20Rafale%20Marine%20Jet%20deal%20just%20ahead%20of%20the%20scheduled%20visit%20of%20Indian%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%20to%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffrance-submits-final-price-offer-to-india-for-26-rafale-marine-jet-deal-6677687%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hurricane%20Helene%20leaves%20'biblical%20devastation'%20in%20North%20Carolina%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727631176000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fdd1f%2Flive%2F46517c70-7e7a-11ef-bda7-e1427314c99f.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcly5d9y07e3o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Homes%20are%20destroyed%2C%20towns%20are%20cut-off%2