%20Crisis%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20left%20Iran%20with%20%26quot%3Ba%20serious%20dilemma%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Vaez%2C%20especially%20that%20the%20group's%20deterrence%20regarding%20Israel%20was%20now%20%26quot%3Bin%20complete%20disarray%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomic%20crisis%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Tehran-based%20international%20relations%20professor%20Mehdi%20Zakerian%2C%20developments%20have%20shown%20that%20the%20Iran-aligned%20resistance%20front%20%26quot%3Bwas%20not%20only%20unable%20to%20contain%20Israel%2C%20it%20also%20suffered%20serious%20blows%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENasrallah's%20death%20came%20around%20two%20months%20after%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas's%20political%20chief%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20was%20killed%20in%20late%20July%20in%20Tehran%20where%20he%20had%20attended%20President%20Masoud%20Pezeshkian's%20inauguration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20blamed%20Israel%20for%20his%20death%20and%20vowed%20to%20retaliate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZakerian%20says%20rebuilding%20Hezbollah%20will%20be%20no%20small%20feat%20for%20Tehran%20amid%20its%20mounting%20economic%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20get%20involved%20in%20reconstructing%20Lebanon%20or%20re-equipping%20Hezbollah%2C%20it%20will%20aggravate%20Iran's%20economic%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20been%20reeling%20from%20the%20economic%20impact%20of%20international%20sanctions%2C%20which%20have%20contributed%20to%20soaring%20inflation%2C%20high%20unemployment%20and%20a%20record%20low%20rate%20for%20the%20Iranian%20rial%20against%20the%20US%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPezeshkian's%20government%20has%20boosted%20efforts%20to%20help%20ease%20the%20crippling%20sanctions%20and%20revive%20a%202015%20landmark%20nuclear%20deal%20which%20collapsed%20when%20the%20United%20States%20unilaterally%20withdrew%20from%20the%20accord%20three%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20have%20said%20Iran%20h