ploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communicate-with-kids-1727526887-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communicate-with-kids-1727526887-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communicate-with-kids-1727526887-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communicate-with-kids-1727526887-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367955%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHelping%20the%20Deaf%20to%20communicate.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20Rupmani%E2%80%99s%20incredible%20struggles%20early%20on%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20remarkable%20that%20years%20later%20she%20would%20go%20on%20to%20co-found%20a%20venture%20called%20SignAble%20Communications%2C%20which%20among%20other%20things%2C%20has%20developed%20an%20app%20that%20provides%20a%20video%20relay%20service%20that%20empowers%20the%20Deaf%20to%20communicate%20and%20express%20themselves%20without%20barriers.%20The%20app%20offers%20Deaf%20persons%20%E2%80%9Caccess%20to%20a%20live%20interpreter%20at%20their%20fingertips%2C%20anytime%20and%20anywhere%2C%20all%20at%20an%20affordable%20price%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20app%2C%20Deaf%20people%20can%20communicate%20with%20essential%20service%20providers%20like%20the%20police%20and%20doctors%2C%20while%20also%20allowing%20them%20to%20communicate%20with%20their%20family%20and%20work%20colleagues.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20the%20remarkable%20story%20of%20how%20she%20found%20herself%20and%20developed%20an%20app%20which%20is%20helping%20open%20up%20different%20worlds%20for%20thousands%20of%20Indians%20who%20cannot%20hear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDiscovering%20her%20identity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20studying%20up%20till%20Class%209%2C%20she%20got%20married%20to%20her%20Deaf%20partner%20and%20they%20moved%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20initially%20saw%20marriage%20as%20a%20way%20to%20address%20my%20challenges%20and%20start%20anew%2C%20which%20led%20me%20to%20move%20to%20Delhi.%20After%20facing%20numerous%20difficulties%20in%20the%20relationship%2C%20I%20made%20the%20difficult%20decision%20to%20return%20home%20but%20my%20family%20didn%E2%80%99t%20approve%20and%20insisted%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20figure%20things%20out%20on%20my%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20her%20divorce%20in%202011%20that%20Rupmani%20resumed%20her%20studies%20and%20went%20on%20to%20finish%20high%20school.%20She%20would%20go%20on%20to%20earn%20a%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20sociology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLiving%20in%20Delhi%20ultimately%20provided%20me%20with%20the%20opportunity%20to%20connect%20with%20other%20Deaf%20individuals%20in%20my%20early%20twenties%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20witnessed%20sign%20language%20being%20used%20among%20the%20Deaf%20community.%20I%20longed%20to%20join%20them%2C%20but%20they%20often%20excluded%20me%20because%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20sign%20language%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20she%20found%20resources%20developed%20by%20organisations%20like%20the%20Noida%20Deaf%20Society%20(NDS)%20and%20%E2%80%98The%20Way%20Deaf%E2%80%99%20to%20learn%20sign%20language%2C%20supplemented%20by%20various%20YouTube%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334578%2Fcoda-child-of-deaf-adult-indian-sign-language-isl%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESign%20language%20is%20the%20native%20language%20of%20the%20Deaf%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20allowing%20individuals%20to%20express%20themselves%20and%20communicate%20authentically%2C%20just%20like%20anyone%20else.%20It%20is%20a%20fundamental%20right%2C%20and%20access%20to%20it%20should%20be%20provided%20from%20a%20young%20age%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssisting%20her%20during%20this%20time%20in%20Delhi%20were%20disability%20rights%20activists%20like%20Geeta%20Sharma%20of%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20the%20Deaf%20(NAD)%20and%20the%20late%20Javed%20Abidi%20from%20the%20National%20Centre%20for%20Promotion%20of%20Employment%20for%20Disabled%20People%20(NCPEDP)%20who%20she%20believes%20played%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpivotal%20role%20in%20helping%20me%20discover%20the%20true%20essence%20of%20knowledge%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20introduced%20me%20to%20the%20Deaf%20community%20and%20other%20specially-abled%20communities%20and%20provided%20invaluable%20guidance%20that%20has%20empowered%20me%20to%20navigate%20the%20world%20with%20confidence.%20I%20am%20deeply%20grateful%20for%20their%20support%20during%20this%20crucial%20phase%20of%20my%20life%3B%20without%20their%20mentorship%2C%20I%20would%20have%20felt%20lost.%20Through%20their%20encouragement%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F101036%2Fdelhi-cafe-hearken-hearing-impaired-staff%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20learned%20sign%20language%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20forged%20meaningful%20friendships%2C%20and%20embarked%20on%20a%20transformative%20journey%20to%20discover%20my%20own%20identity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20brief%20stint%20with%20the%20NAD%2C%20she%20began%20working%20with%20HAQ%3A%20Centre%20for%20Child%20Rights%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20non-profit.%20Her%20nearly%20six-year%20stint%20at%20HAQ%20landed%20her%20an%20opportunity%20to%20work%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20Development%20Programme%20(UNDP)%20in%202017%20in%20Europe%20where%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20she%20discovered%20the%20transformative%20impact%20of%20Video%20Relay%20Service%20(VRS)%20for%20the%20Deaf.%3C%2Fp%3E