ing%20that%20came%20my%20way.%20I%20moved%20to%20Ukraine%20and%20travelled%20across%20Europe%2C%20where%20I%20was%20amazed%20by%20the%20robust%20access%20to%20sign%20language%20in%20other%20countries%2C%20especially%20the%20availability%20of%20technology%20like%20VRS.%20This%20exposure%20allowed%20me%20to%20learn%20and%20grow%20in%20ways%20I%20had%20never%20imagined.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESignAble%20for%20the%20Deaf%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20her%20time%20in%20Europe%2C%20Rupmani%20came%20back%20to%20India.%20While%20looking%20for%20a%20job%2C%20she%20encountered%20Tarun%20Sarwal%2C%20who%20also%20returned%20to%20India%20after%20spending%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20working%20with%20humanitarian%20organisations%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20first%20met%20Mr%20Tarun%20while%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20job%20after%20returning%20from%20my%20work%20at%20the%20UN.%20A%20common%20friend%20introduced%20us%20online%2C%20and%20during%20our%20initial%20conversations%2C%20Tarun%20asked%20how%20I%20could%20contribute%20to%20supporting%20people%20with%20disabilities.%20After%20many%20discussions%20about%20potential%20projects%20and%20ideas%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20meet%20in%20person.%20Our%20first%20face-to-face%20meeting%20took%20place%20on%201%20January%2C%202019%2C%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20amidst%20the%20Deaf%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20his%20time%20working%20in%20Geneva%20with%20an%20international%20humanitarian%20organisation%20that%20Tarun%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20difference%20an%20interpreter%20could%20make%20in%20a%20Deaf%20person%E2%80%99s%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communications-Team-1727527431.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SignAble%20Communications%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communications-Team-1727527431.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communications-Team-1727527431-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communications-Team-1727527431-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communications-Team-1727527431-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communications-Team-1727527431-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367960%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESignAble%20Communications%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUpon%20my%20return%20to%20India%2C%20the%20first%20thought%20that%20crossed%20my%20mind%20was%20how%20to%20establish%20better%20access%20to%20sign%20language.%20Fortunately%2C%20I%20met%20Tarun%20Sarwal%2C%20who%20also%20had%20the%20idea%20of%20working%20with%20the%20Deaf.%20At%20first%2C%20he%20employed%20me%20to%20understand%20what%20exactly%20the%20needs%20were%20of%20the%20Deaf%20community.%20To%20communicate%20with%20each%20other%20we%20needed%20an%20interpreter%20and%20in%20the%20process%2C%20I%20taught%20him%20sign%20language%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20they%20came%20up%20with%20an%20idea%20to%20develop%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20abroad%2C%20I%20received%20comprehensive%20access%20to%20information%20and%20resources%20that%20significantly%20aided%20my%20progress.%20I%20wanted%20every%20Deaf%20individual%20like%20me%20to%20have%20the%20same%20opportunity%20to%20succ