al%20to%20initiate%20these%20efforts%20early%20by%20engaging%20adolescents%20in%20discussions%20about%20sexual%20and%20reproductive%20health%20and%20rights.%20Additionally%2C%20strategic%20engagement%20is%20needed%20to%20encourage%20men%20to%20consider%20vasectomy%20as%20a%20viable%20family%20planning%20option%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20we%20get%20there%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonam%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20that%20male%20engagement%20intervention%20needs%20a%20multi-sectoral%20approach.%20Education%2C%20age%20at%20marriage%2C%20health-seeking%20behaviour%2C%20and%20socio-cultural%20norms%20need%20to%20be%20addressed%20simultaneously%20and%20concurrently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20two%20steps%20she%20recommends%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFrontline%20health%20workers%20(ASHAs%2C%20ANMs)%20must%20be%20supported%20and%20male%20health%20workers%20must%20be%20added%20to%20supplement%20the%20existing%20workforce.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGiven%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20present%20emphasis%20on%20strengthening%20counselling%20at%20hospitals%2C%20an%20increased%20thrust%20on%20couples%20counselling%20and%20follow-ups%20is%20likely%20to%20bear%20fruit.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22What%20is%20the%20right%20solution%20for%20couples%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367538%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Image%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2FIndianFaces%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Government%E2%80%99s%20effort%20to%20engage%20male%20peer%20educators%20as%20part%20of%20the%20RKSK%20(Rashtriya%20Kishor%20Swasthya%20Karyakram)%20programme%20is%20a%20move%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLastly%2C%20the%20involvement%20of%20other%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20private%20partners%2C%20to%20involve%20men%20in%20this%20process%20needs%20to%20be%20underlined.%20Innovative%20ways%20to%20ensure%20this%20under%20existing%20PPP%20(public-private%20partnership)%20and%20social%20franchising%20models%20will%20positively%20impact%20health%20and%20family%20planning%20at%20the%20community%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20is%20male%20participation%20crucial%20in%20family%20planning%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20believes%20that%20if%20you%20already%20have%20a%20child%20and%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20intend%20to%20have%20another%2C%20getting%20a%20vasectomy%20is%20a%20must%20so%20that%20you%20can%20move%20on%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20have%20decided%20not%20to%20have%20children%20at%20all%2C%20my%20suggestion%20is%20to%20take%2018%20months%20as%20a%20couple%20to%20discuss%20this%20in%20honest%20detail%2C%20do%20the%20research%2C%20talk%20to%20experts%2C%20understand%20what%20it%20is%20to%20be%20a%20parent%20and%20have%20those%20delicate%20conversations%20with%20your%20family.%20Once%20you%20are%20clear%20about%20this%20decision%2C%20get%20the%20procedure%20done%20and%20move%20on%20ahead%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20Poonam%20notes%20that%20the%20discourse%20on%20the%20engagement%20of%20men%20as%20partners%20in%20accessing%20family%20planning%20and%20health%20services%20needs%20to%20go%20beyond%20contraceptive%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMale%20participation%20is%20about%20being%20responsible%20and%20respecting%20equality%20rather%20than%20just%20about%20decision-making.%20It%20should%20extend%20to%20the%20role%20of%20men%20as%20enablers%20and%20beneficiaries%20in%20the%20process%20of%20ensuring%20dignity%2C%20equal%20voice%2C%20and%20reproductive%20rights%20for%20women.%20Male%20participation%20should%20not%20mean%20that%20women%E2%80%99s%20decision-making%20powers%20are%20encumbered%2C%20and%20women%20are%20forced%20to%20accept%20men%E2%80%99s%20choices%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStudies%20reveal%20that%20men%20often%20control%20contraception%20decision-making%20and%20decision%20of%20contraception%20of%20female%20partners%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20prevalence%20of%20intimate%20partner%20violence%2C%20which%20can%20impede%20contraceptive%20use%20as%20well%20as%20increase%20the%20risk%20for%20contraceptive%20failure.%20Male%20engagement%20in%20family%20planning%20should%20improve%20men%E2%80%99s%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20reproductive%20health%20and%20promote%20gender%20equality%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727275238000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-2-1727271677.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367509%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Mumbai-based%20couple%20chose%20a%20vasectomy%20after%20deciding%20not%20to%20have%20children%2C%20breaking%20societal%20norms.%20Their%20decision%20came%20after%20extensive%20discussions%2C%20research%2C%20and%20consultations%20with%20doctors.%20Highlighting%20the%20simplicity%20of%20the%20procedure%20and%20societal%20challenges%2C%20they%20advocate%20for%20more%20men%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20family%20planning%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367509%2Fworld-contraception-day-why-more-indian-men-should-get-vasectomy-family-planning%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Be%20Kind%E2%80%99%3A%20What%20Toxic%20Workplaces%20Can%20Learn%20From%20Companies%20Building%20Healthy%20Environments%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20hope%20my%20child%E2%80%99s%20experience%20leads%20to%20real%20change%20so%20that%20no%20other%20family%20has%20to%20endure%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F265281%2Frajani-jagtap-mumbai-doctor-online-grief-counselling%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrief%20and%20trauma%3C%2Fa%3E%20we%20are%20going%20through.%20My%20Anna%20is%20no%20longer%20with%20us%2C%20but%20her%20story%20can%20still%20make%20a%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Anita%20Augustine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20heart-wrenching%20words%20come%20from%20a%20mother%20grieving%20the%20loss%20of%20her%20daughter%2C%20Anna%20Sebastian%20Perayil%2C%20who%20passed%20away%20in%20July%202024.%20A%20chartered%20accountant%20at%20EY%20(Ernst%20%26amp%3B%20Young)%20India%2C%20Anna%E2%80%99s%20mother%20claims%20her%20death%20was%20caused%20by%20overwhelming%20work%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnna%20had%20only%20begun