ey%20were%20the%20first%20to%20come%20up%20with%20flattened%20balls%20with%20stuffing%20of%20%3Cem%3Emoong%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(lentils)%2C%20which%20they%20say%20was%20the%20predecessor%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263555%2Fbest-homemade-bihar-food-dishes-delhi-women-lockdown-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emodern-day%20%3Cem%3Ekachori%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20for%20now%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20dive%20deep%20into%20the%20city%20that%20is%20most%20associated%20with%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekachori%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Here%20are%20some%20spots%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebest%20kachori%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Jaipur%20loved%20by%20locals%20and%20hailed%20by%20foodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Sampat%20Namkeen%20Bhandar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20crowd%20favourite%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Jaipur%20%3Cem%3Ekachori%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Sampat%20Namkeen%20Bhandar%20dates%20back%20to%201936%20and%20is%20currently%20helmed%20by%20the%20fourth%20generation%20of%20the%20family.%20A%20standout%20at%20Sampat%20is%20the%20spicy%20%3Cem%3Ealoo%20ki%20kachori%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20potato%20filling%20inside%20a%20deep-fried%20dough%20ball)%2C%20which%20is%20prepared%20without%20removing%20the%20potato%20skins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726651427.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sampat%20Namkeen%20Bhandar%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20iconic%20spots%20for%20a%20feast%20of%20kachoris%20in%20Jaipur%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726651427.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossi