%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-9-1726671327-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-9-1726671327-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366621%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Kalpana%20Sankar%20was%20the%20recipient%20of%20the%20Nari%20Shakti%20Puraskar%20in%202016%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20rural%20credit%20accounted%20for%20only%2020.8%20percent%20(Rs%2011.99%20lakh%20crore)%20of%20the%20Rs%2057.58%20lakh%20crore%20sanctioned%20by%20NBFCs%20in%202021.%20This%20highlights%20the%20urban-rural%20divide%20in%20access%20to%20credit.%20Thus%2C%20when%20designing%20a%20blueprint%20for%20the%20job%20creation%20model%2C%20Dr%20Sankar%20says%20facilitating%20access%20to%20economic%20capital%20was%20prime.%20She%20decided%20to%20keep%20financial%20independence%20for%20women%20at%20the%20fore.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20ensured%20this%20while%20providing%20them%20%5Bthe%20women%5D%20skill%20training%20to%20hone%20their%20entrepreneurial%20ability%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20The%20module%20rests%20on%20the%20backbone%20that%20credit%20alone%20will%20not%20suffice.%20Skill%20training%20and%20coaching%20are%20vital%20to%20sustaining%20a%20business.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20so%2C%20we%20train%20these%20women%20in%20group%20dynamics%2C%20benefits%20of%20savings%2C%20interest%20computation%2C%20and%20financial%20and%20functional%20literacy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%2C%20adding%20that%20watching%20the%20women%20grow%20from%20strength%20to%20strength%20and%20relish%20their%20newfound%20independence%20thrills%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20World%20Bank%20report%20underscores%20how%2079%20percent%20of%20rural%20households%20do%20not%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F32