%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-1726841838-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-1726841838-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-1726841838-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366938%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESunil%20Jaglan%20is%20a%20social%20activist%20who%20advocates%20against%20female%20foeticide%20and%20girl-child%20inequality.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20the%20birth%20of%20his%20baby%20girl%20that%20compelled%20him%20to%20digress%20from%20his%20focus%20on%20village%20development%20to%20female%20foeticide.%20%E2%80%9CI%20never%20imagined%20this%20path%20for%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reminisces%2C%20thinking%20back%20to%20his%20days%20as%20a%20mathematics%20coach%20in%20his%20early%2020s%20when%20working%20Sundays%20and%20the%20extra%20money%20was%20all%20he%20looked%20forward%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20youth%20with%20simple%20dreams%2C%20Jaglan%20has%20grown%20into%20the%20proud%20father%20of%20two%20daughters%3B%20teaching%20India%E2%80%99s%20generation%20of%20men%20to%20be%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20baby%20girl%20melts%20a%20patriarch%E2%80%99s%20heart%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20every%20question%20I%20pose%20to%20Jaglan%2C%20I%20can%20hear%20two%20background%20voices%20nudging%20him%20when%20he%20muddles%20the%20details.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20school%20holiday%20for%20Nandini%20(12)%20and%20Yachika%20(10).%20Naturally%2C%20they%20have%20picked%20a%20spot%20beside%20their%20father%20for%20the%20interview.%20Having%20had%20a%20front-row%20seat%20to%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335631%2Fassam-jorhat-transwoman-opens-free-libraries-for-queer-positivity-lgbt-empowerment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D