ry.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKoi%20baat%20nahi%2C%20agli%20baar%20ladka%20hoga%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Don%E2%80%99t%20worry.%20Next%20time%20you%20will%20get%20a%20son).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FrA-F2BWnHmk%3Fsi%3DN_7a_Xus1lNQBnDd%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20how%20would%20Jaglan%20respond%20to%20these%20unwarranted%20sympathies%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20and%20bought%20more%20%3Cem%3Emithai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20celebrated%20for%20a%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20I%20went%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F244172%2Fchushul-village-ladakh-doctor-jigmet-wangchuk-line-of-actual-control-india-china-border-coronavirus-hero-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evillage%20health%20centre%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20check%20on%20the%20sex%20ratio.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20832%20females%20per%201%2C000%20males%20in%202011.%20Some%20fact-checking%20on%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20sex%20ratio%20through%20the%20years%20tells%20me%20Jaglan%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20surprised%20at%20the%20numbers.%20The%20state%20has%20been%20(in)famous%20for%20having%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20sex%20ratios%20in%20India%20%E2%80%94%20a%20problem%20compounded%20by%20patriarchal%20mindsets%20prevalent%20in%20North%20India%20where%20raising%20a%20girl%20has%20sacrificial%20connotations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%202023%20statistics%20point%20out%2C%20that%20mindsets%20are%20seeing%20a%20shift%20%E2%80%94%20there%20were%20916%20females%20per%201%2C000%20males.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20however%2C%20Jaglan%20was%20horrified.%20He%20intended%20to%20discuss%20this%20issue%20with%20women%20at%20the%20next%20%3Cem%3Egram%20sabha%3C