-element-caption%5C%22%3ESunil%20Jaglan%20encouraged%20women%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekhap%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Bibipur%20to%20participate%20in%20village%20decisions.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirm%20in%20his%20resolve%20to%20change%20this%20chauvinist%20mentality%2C%20Jaglan%20says%20he%20began%20urging%20women%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20%3Cem%3Echaupals%20%3C%2Fem%3E(village%20meetings)%2C%20supported%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20sisters%2C%20and%20mother.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202012%2C%20we%20set%20up%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20women%20%3Cem%3Egram%20sabhas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20The%20ripple%20effect%20this%20had%20was%20tremendous%2C%20and%20Jaglan%20decided%20to%20go%20a%20step%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20hosted%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekhap%20panchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202012%20in%20Bibipur.%20An%20unofficial%20meeting%20of%20clans%20across%20villages%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekhap%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20historically%20headed%20and%20attended%20by%20men.%20But%20the%20one%20that%20Jaglan%20hosted%20saw%202%2C000%20women%20from%20across%20India%20convene%20to%20discuss%20the%20issues%20that%20oppressed%20their%20female%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20historic%20win!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20issues%20discussed%20were%20domestic%20violence%2C%20%3Cem%3Edowry%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20payment%20given%20to%20the%20groom%20by%20the%20bride%E2%80%99s%20family%20during%20marriage)%2C%20and%20pressure%20to%20abort%20baby%20girl%20foetuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20effects%20of%20the%20Bibipur%20model%20have%20trickled%20into%20Gurugram.%20As%20Ramchander%2C%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20Makhrola%20village%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20model%20of%20village%20development%20was%20introduced%20in%20our%20village%20a%20year%20ago.%20While%20on%20paper%2C%20women%20had%20an%20equal%20participation%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%